OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSteve Wright gets new      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FSaturday Radio 2 show      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Steve Wright is to present a second    
OL,6, show every weekend on BBC Radio 2 - a  
OL,7, year after signing off from his weekday
OL,8, afternoon slot after 23 years.         
OL,10,FHe will take over Saturday lunchtime   
OL,11,Fshow Pick of the Pops from fellow      
OL,12,Fveteran Paul Gambaccini, who is moving 
OL,13,Fto a new show on Sunday evenings.      
OL,15,FWright has continued to present his    
OL,16,Flong-running Sunday Love Songs show    
OL,17,Fover the past year.                    
OL,19,FHe said Pick of the Pops - which runs  
OL,20,Fdown past charts - was "legendary".    
